I"<blockquote>
  <p>To hold a package:</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="code-header">
    <button class="copy-code-button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"></button>
</div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ sudo apt-mark hold &lt;package&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>or</p>

<div class="code-header">
    <button class="copy-code-button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"></button>
</div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>echo &lt;package&gt; hold | sudo dpkg --set-selections
</code></pre></div></div>
<blockquote>
  <p>To unhold a package:</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="code-header">
    <button class="copy-code-button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"></button>
</div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ sudo apt-mark unhold &lt;package&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>or</p>

<div class="code-header">
    <button class="copy-code-button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"></button>
</div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>echo &lt;package&gt; install | sudo dpkg --set-selections
</code></pre></div></div>
